#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; header_font=&#8221;Poppins||||||||&#8221; header_text_color=&#8221;#0C71C3&#8243; header_font_size=&#8221;45px&#8221; custom_margin=&#8221;||10px||false|false&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h1>Dr. Debojyoti De<\/h1>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.10.3&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; header_5_font=&#8221;Poppins||||||||&#8221; header_5_text_color=&#8221;#000000&#8243; header_5_font_size=&#8221;18px&#8221; header_5_line_height=&#8221;1.5em&#8221; custom_margin=&#8221;||0px||false|false&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h5>Assistant Professor<br \/>\nDepartment of Biotechnology<br \/>\nNational Institute Of Technology, Durgapur<\/h5>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.10.3&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; header_5_font=&#8221;Poppins||||||||&#8221; header_5_text_color=&#8221;#000000&#8243; header_5_font_size=&#8221;18px&#8221; header_5_line_height=&#8221;1.5em&#8221; custom_margin=&#8221;|0px|0px||false|false&#8221; custom_padding=&#8221;0px||||false|false&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h5 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Debojyoti De graduated from Samsung Biomedical Research Institute, Sungkyunkwan University\u00a0School of Medicine, South Korea with PhD in Molecular Cell Biology with specialization in Regenerative Medicine. He is a Stem cell Biologist by training and possesses a vast experience in handling multidimensional genomics and epigenetics data, especially in dissecting complex biological mechanisms of cellular fate change and also to understand metabolic disorders. After the completion of his PhD degree, he worked as a Post-Doctoral Fellow and subsequently as Research Professor at Sungkyunkwan University School of Medicine.<\/h5>\n<h2><\/h2>\n<h2><strong>Current Position<\/strong><\/h2>\n<h5 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Assistant Professor, Department of Biotechnology, National Institute of Technology Durgapur (Jan 2019).<\/h5>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][et_pb_button button_url=&#8221;https:\/\/scholar.google.ca\/citations?hl=en&amp;view_op=list_works&amp;gmla=AJsN-F6Oc-qZTlRVeLLIPj3hDcPW5h6vOlR0ob7xUF1bB4t76zyc0_J_8fo3ZkomwbZjsjq4cdHcWRMAc-B72awneZ8MxpcIPsA2oj4gdX9N8DhDYQlz6-0&amp;user=Y9QupNUAAAAJ&#8221; button_text=&#8221;Google Scholar&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.10.3&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; custom_button=&#8221;on&#8221; button_text_size=&#8221;18px&#8221; button_text_color=&#8221;#ffffff&#8221; button_bg_color=&#8221;#E09900&#8243; button_border_width=&#8221;0px&#8221; button_border_color=&#8221;RGBA(0,0,0,0)&#8221; button_border_radius=&#8221;50px&#8221; button_font=&#8221;Poppins||||||||&#8221; button_icon=&#8221;%%119%%&#8221; custom_margin=&#8221;10px||||false|false&#8221; custom_padding=&#8221;6px|40px|6px|40px|true|true&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221; button_bg_color__hover_enabled=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; button_bg_color__hover=&#8221;#E09900&#8243; button_bg_enable_color__hover=&#8221;on&#8221; button_text_color__hover_enabled=&#8221;on|hover&#8221; button_text_color__hover=&#8221;#FFFFFF&#8221;][\/et_pb_button][\/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=&#8221;2_5&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.10.3&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_image src=&#8221;http:\/\/ddelabs.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/20240315_185904_copy-1.jpg&#8221; title_text=&#8221;20240315_185904_copy&#8221; align=&#8221;right&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.10.3&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; transform_scale=&#8221;105%|105%&#8221; width=&#8221;87%&#8221; max_width=&#8221;100%&#8221; height=&#8221;442px&#8221; custom_margin=&#8221;20px|77px|-35px|77px|false|true&#8221; hover_enabled=&#8221;0&#8243; border_radii=&#8221;off|50%|50%|50%|50%&#8221; border_radii_tablet=&#8221;&#8221; border_radii_phone=&#8221;&#8221; border_radii_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; global_col